[[File:Museu Nacional, Coleção WERNER.jpg|thumb|Showcase of the Werner Collection display.]] [[File:Museu Nacional exibe coleção de minerais da Família Real (38154979055).jpg|thumb|Example of amethyst quartz of the Werner Collection.]] The '''Werner Collection''' is one of the collections on display at the [[National Museum of Brazil]], in [[Rio de Janeiro]]. The collection gathers around 60 rare minerals obtained in the [[18th century]] from the [[Freiberg University of Mining and Technology|Freiberg Mining Academy]], Germany, by the Portuguese nobleman [[António de Araújo e Azevedo, 1st Count of Barca|António de Araújo e Azevedo]]. The name of the collection is due to the main researcher of the German academy, scientist [[Abraham Gottlob Werner]]. The collection came to Brazil in the 19th century, brought by the Royal Family, who was escaping from the Napoleonic invasion, and was initially sent to the [[Instituto Militar de Engenharia|Royal Military Academy]], being moved to the Royal Museum (former name of the National Museu) in 1819. It is considered that it was the first collection to compose the National Museum.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://agenciabrasil.ebc.com.br/cultura/noticia/2017-12/museu-nacional-exibe-coleacao-de-minerais-da-familia-real-portuguesa|title=Museu Nacional exibe coleção de minerais da Família Real portuguesa|last=Virgilio|first=Paulo|date=2017-12-13|work=Agência Brasil|access-date=2018-09-25|language=pt-br|trans-title=National Museum displays collection of minerals of the Portuguese Royal Family}}</ref>
This collection was stuck by the [[National Museum of Brazil fire|fire of 2018 at the National Museum]], but it was reported that its restoration will be possible.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://brasil.estadao.com.br/noticias/geral,parte-da-colecao-werner-e-resgatada-do-museu-nacional-diz-professor-da-ufrj,70002486187|title=Parte da coleção Werner é resgatada do Museu Nacional, diz professor da UFRJ - Brasil - Estadão|last=Grellet|first=Fábio|date=2018-09-03|work=Estadão|access-date=2018-09-25|language=pt-br|trans-title=Part of the Werner Collection is rescued from the National Museum, says UFRJ teacher - Brazil - Estadão}}</ref>
